말"}],"status":"Ended","tagline":"","type":"Miniseries","vote_average":7.1,"vote_count":11}},"person_85477_translations":{"at":1773688718713,"data":{"id":85477,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Tracy Darrell \"Trace\" Adkins (born January 13, 1962) is an American country music artist. He made his debut in 1996 with the album Dreamin' Out Loud, released on Capitol Records Nashville. Since then, Adkins has released seven more studio albums and two Greatest Hits compilations. In addition, he has charted more than twenty singles on the Billboard country music charts, including the Number One hits \"(This Ain't) No Thinkin' Thing\", \"Ladies Love Country Boys\", and \"You're Gonna Miss This\", which peaked in 1997, 2007, and 2008, respectively. \"I Left Something Turned on at Home\" went to #1 on Canada's country chart. All but one of his studio albums have received gold or platinum certification in the United States; his highest-selling to date is 2005's Songs About Me, which has been certified 2× Multi-Platinum for shipping two million copies.\n\nHe has also made several appearances on television, including as a panelist on the game shows Hollywood Squares and Pyramid, as a finalist on The Celebrity Apprentice, as the voice for recurring character Elvin on King of the Hill, and in television commercial voice-overs for the KFC restaurant chain. In addition, Adkins has written an autobiography entitled A Personal Stand: Observations and Opinions from a Free-Thinking Roughneck, which was released in late 2007.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Trace Adkins, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Trace Adkins","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_72673_translations":{"at":1773688721480,"data":{"id":72673,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Irene Montalà","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Irene Montalà (18 de julio de 1976) es una actriz española conocida principalmente por su participación en series de televisión como El internado, El barco y La verdad entre otras.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Irene Montalà","primary":true}}]}},"person_1614218_translations":{"at":1773688727152,"data":{"id":1614218,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Tan Song Yun, or Seven, is an award-winning actor, singer and model born in Luzhou, Sichuan, China. A graduate of Beijing Film Academy, she got her start as a child actor in 2005 when she filmed the TV series “Wild Chrysanthemum” (山菊花). It was in the 2005 series \"Live Your Days Peacefully\" (好好过日子), however, that audiences first saw her.\n\nIn 2016, following her performance in \"The Whirlwind Girl\" (旋风少女), Song Yun snagged the Best New Actress award at the 22nd Huading Awards, earning her second Huading award—this time Best Actress—for \"Under the Power\" (锦衣之下). For her work on \"The Fox's Summer\" (狐狸的夏天), she won the award for Best Actress in a web series at both the 2nd Asia New Media Film Festival and the 2nd Golden Gudeo Media Awards in 2017.","name":"Tan Songyun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"谭松韵，原名谭晶晶，演员，毕业于北京电影学院表演系。\n\n2001年，进入四川省舞蹈学校学习古典舞和民间舞。2005年，因拍摄电视剧《好好过日子》而接触表演 。2007年考入北京电影学院表演系。2012年，因在清宫剧《后宫·甄嬛传》中扮演淳贵人一角而受到关注。2016年，凭借网络剧《最好的我们》获得爱奇艺尖叫之夜年度最具潜力演员；同年，她参演的爱情电影《微微一笑很倾城》上映  。2017年，凭借爱情偶像剧《狐狸的夏天》获得第二届金海鸥亚洲新媒体电影节网剧最佳女主角奖及第二届金骨朵网络影视盛典最佳女主角奖；同年，由她领衔主演的青春励志偶像剧《浪花一朵朵》播出后收视率多次破1；同年，参加演技竞演类励志综艺《演员的诞生》 。\n\n2019年10月17日，入选2019福布斯中国30位30岁以下精英榜 ；同年，主演的悬疑纯爱钜制《锦衣之下》上线播出。2020年8月10日，主演的青春成长治愈剧《以家人之名》播出。9月，凭借《以家人之名》获得第4届网影盛典年度最佳剧集女演员 。","name":"谭松韵","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"譚松韻","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"담송운","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Đàm Tùng Vận (Tiếng Trung: 谭松韵; bính âm: Tánsōngyùn; sinh ngày 31 tháng 5 năm 1990) là một nữ diễn viên người Trung Quốc, từng là một ngôi sao nhí. Cô được khán giả biết đến đầu tiên qua vai Phương Thuần Ý trong phim Hậu cung Chân Hoàn truyện. Cô tốt nghiệp đại học chuyên ngành Biểu diễn tại Học viện Điện ảnh Bắc Kinh năm 2009.","name":"Đàm Tùng Vận","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тань Сун Юнь","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"譚松韻，原名譚晶晶，演員，畢業於北京電影學院表演系。\n\n2001 年，進入四川省舞蹈學校學習古典舞和民間舞。2005 年，因拍攝電視劇《好好過日子》而接觸表演 。2007 年考入北京電影學院表演系。2012 年，因在清宮劇《後宮·甄嬛傳》中扮演淳貴人一角而受到關注。2016 年，憑藉網絡劇《最好的我們》獲得愛奇藝尖叫之夜年度最具潛力演員；同年，她參演的愛情電影《微微一笑很傾城》上映 。2017 年，憑藉愛情偶像劇《狐狸的夏天》獲得第二屆金海鷗亞洲新媒體電影節網劇最佳女主角獎及第二屆金骨朵網絡影視盛典最佳女主角獎；同年，由她領銜主演的青春勵志偶像劇《浪花一朵朵》播出後收視率多次破 1；同年，參加演技競演類勵志綜藝《演員的誕生》 。\n\n2019 年 10 月 17 日，入選 2019 福布斯中國 30 位 30 歲以下精英榜 ；同年，主演的懸疑純愛鉅制《錦衣之下》上線播出。2020 年 8 月 10 日，主演的青春成長治癒劇《以家人之名》播出。9 月，憑藉《以家人之名》獲得第 4 屆網影盛典年度最佳劇集女演員 。","name":"譚松韻","primary":false}}]}},"person_51988_translations":{"at":1773688732018,"data":{"id":51988,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Elizabeth Anne Caplan (born June 30, 1982) is an American actress. Her performances as Virginia E. Johnson in the Showtime series Masters of Sex (2013–2016) and as Libby Epstein in FX on Hulu's Fleishman Is in Trouble (2022) have earned her nominations at the Primetime Emmy Awards.\n\nHer first acting role was on the television series Freaks and Geeks (1999–2000). Since then, she had series-regular roles in several television series including Related (2005–2006), Party Down (2009–2010; 2023), Das Boot (2018), Castle Rock (2019), Truth Be Told (2019), Fatal Attraction (2023), and Zero Day (2025).\n\nCaplan's film breakthrough came with her role as Janis Ian in Mean Girls (2004). Her other film appearances include My Best Friend's Girl (2008) Cloverfield (2008), Hot Tub Time Machine, 127 Hours (both 2010), Save the Date, Bachelorette (both 2012), The Interview (2014), Now You See Me 2, Allied (both 2016), and Cobweb (2023).\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Lizzy Caplan, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Lizzy Caplan","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Elizabeth \"Lizzy\" Caplan urodziła się 30 czerwca 1982 roku w Los Angeles, w stanie Kalifornia. Tam też mieszka. W 2000 roku ukończyła prestiżową Hamilton Academy of Music w Los Angeles. Chodziła do jednej klasy razem z aktorem Emile Hirsch. W 2002 r. zagrała w filmie \"Kwaśne pomarańcze\", obok takich aktorów jak Jack Black i Colin Hanks. Jeszcze w tym samym roku pojawiła się w niezależnej produkcji \"Hardcore Action News\". Później dostała rolę nastoletniej córki w serialu \"The Pitts\" (2003 r.), oraz wystąpiła gościnnie m.in. w \"Tajemnicach Smallville\", \"Once And Again\", \"Luzakach i kujonach\", czy też \"Tru Calling\". W 2004 roku pojawiła się znów na dużym ekranie jako Janis w filmie \"Wredne dziewczyny\".","name":"Lizzy Caplan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"リジー・キャプラン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"丽兹·卡潘（Lizzy Caplan），1982年6月30日出生于美国加利福尼亚州洛杉矶，美国影视演员。\n\n1999年，在学期间参演个人首部电视剧《怪胎与书呆》 。2002年，参演喜剧电影《橘子郡男孩》。2006年，在惊悚电影《爱情是毒药》中饰演萨拉。2008年，凭借科幻电影《科洛弗档案》提名第34届土星奖最佳女配角。2010年，出演科幻喜剧电影《热浴盆时光机》，她凭借该片提名第12届青少年选择奖最佳喜剧片女演员。2013年，由其主演的电视剧《性爱大师第一季》首播，她凭借该剧提名电视评论家选择奖最佳剧情剧女演员、第66届艾美奖选择奖最佳剧情女演员。2016年，由其出演的动作喜剧电影《惊天魔盗团2》上映。2021年，参与配音的动画片《阴谋职场第一季》首播。","name":"丽兹·卡潘","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar","english_name":"Hungarian","data":{"biography":"Elizabeth Anne Caplan (Los Angeles, Kalifornia, 1982. június 30. –) amerikai színésznő.\n\nIsmertebb szerepei közé tartozik Virginia E. Johnson megformálása a Masters of Sex című televíziós sorozatban, mellyel Primetime Emmy-díjra jelölték legjobb női főszereplő (drámasorozat) kategóriában. 2016-ban Lulát alakította a Szemfényvesztők 2. című mozifilmben.\n\nLizzy Caplan 1982. június 30-án született Elizabeth Anne Caplanként a kaliforniai Los Angelesben, zsidó származású családba, Barbara Bragman politikai segéd és Richard Caplan ügyvéd legfiatalabb gyermekeként. Két idősebb testvére van, Julie és Benjamin (Ben). 13 éves volt, amikor édesanyja megbetegedett és meghalt. A gyász hatására gondolt rá először, hogy színésznő legyen. Lizzy a Alexander Hamilton High School-ban tanult, ahol megmutatta érdeklődését a színészt iránt azzal, hogy iskolai színdarabokban játszott. Végül 15 évesen kezdett színészkedni, a nagy áttörés viszont csak pár évvel később, a Különcök és stréberek című televíziós sorozatban jött el, amiben visszatérő szerepet kapott. Diplomáját a rangos Los Angeles-i egyetemen, a Hamilton Academy of Music-ban szerezte, osztálytársa volt a színész Emile Hirsch. Bár kezdetben a zongorázásra fektette a hangsúlyt a színészkedéssel szemben, később áttért a színészet tanulására. Az egyetemen az iskola focicsapatának is tagja volt. 2013-ban komoly szerepet kapott, hiszen beválogatták a Masters of Sex című drámasorozatba, ahol Virginia Johnsont alakítja. A sorozatot 2013-tól 2016-ig sugározták. 2014 november elején bejelentették, hogy Caplan szerepet kap a nagysikerű Szemfényvesztők (Now You See Me) című film folytatásában; Lulát, az új \"Lovast\" játssza. Ekkor jelentették be Daniel Radcliffe szereplését is a filmben.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"리지 캐플런","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Лиззи Каплан","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ліззі Каплан","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Лізі Каплан","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"麗茲·卡潘（Lizzy Caplan），1982 年 6 月 30 日出生於美國加利福尼亞州洛杉磯，美國影視演員。\n\n1999 年，在學期間參演個人首部電視劇《怪胎與書呆》 。2002 年，參演喜劇電影《橘子郡男孩》。2006 年，在驚悚電影《愛情是毒藥》中飾演薩拉。2008 年，憑藉科幻電影《末世兇煞》提名第 34 屆土星獎最佳女配角。2010 年，出演科幻喜劇電影《冰火時光機之回到 80 後》，她憑藉該片提名第 12 屆青少年選擇獎最佳喜劇片女演員。2013 年，由其主演的電視劇《性愛大師第一季》首播，她憑藉該劇提名電視評論家選擇獎最佳劇情劇女演員、第 66 屆艾美獎選擇獎最佳劇情女演員。2016 年，由其出演的動作喜劇電影《驚天魔盜團 2》上映。2021 年，參與配音的動畫片《陰謀職場第一季》首播。","name":"麗茲·卡潘","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"ליזי קפלן","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"LV","iso_639_1":"lv","name":"Latviešu","english_name":"Latvian","data":{"biography":"Elizabete Ena Kaplana (angļu: Elizabeth Anne Caplan; dzimusi 1982. gada 30. jūnijā Losandželosā, Kalifornijā, ASV) ir ebreju izcelsmes amerikāņu aktrise.\n\nKaplanas pirmā aktrises loma bija televīzijas seriālā Freaks and Geeks (1999—2000). Kopš tā laika viņai ir bijušas dažāda lieluma lomas vairākos televīzijas seriālos, tostarp, \"Smolvila. Leģenda par Supermenu\" (2001—2003), \"Īstās asinis\" (2008), \"Jauniņā\" (2012) un Zero Day (2025). Par lomām Showtime seriālā \"Seksa meistari\" (2013—2016) un FX on Hulu seriālā Fleishman Is in Trouble (2022) Lizija Kaplana tikusi nominēta Primetime Emmy balvām.\n\nAtpazīstamību ieguvusi ar Dženisas lomu filmā \"Nekrietneles\" (2004). Piedalījusies filmās \"Orindžas apgabals\" (2002), \"Mana labākā drauga meitene\" (2008), \"Nezvērs\" (2008), \"Burbuļvannas laika mašīna\", \"127 stundas\" (abas 2010. gadā), Item 47, Save the Date, \"Vecmeitas\" (visas 2012. gadā), \"Intervija ar diktatoru\" (2014), \"Sekss, narkotikas un zvaniņš skan\" (2015), \"Krāpšanas ilūzija 2\", \"Sabiedrotie\" (abas 2016. gadā), \"Katastrofu mākslinieks\" (2017), \"Zirnekļtīkls\" (2023) un \"Krāpšanas ilūzija 3\" (2025).","name":"Lizija Kaplana","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"لیزی کپلن","primary":false}}]}},"person_1615316_translations":{"at":1773688732875,"data":{"id":1615316,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Lee Hak-joo is a South Korean actor. He is best known for his roles in the television series The World of the Married, My Name and Newtopia.","name":"Lee Hak-ju","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이학주","pr